The SDK for Project RSO024, Softpay by Softpay ApS,has been successfully created and is now available.Please ensure that you read the document titled "START HERE" before beginning any code development processes. The START HERE document provides critical connectivity data for your application as well as information regarding how to best utilize the specification, sample code, integration guides, and reference guides also contained in the SDK. The IDs that will be required for testing (TPP ID, MID, TID, Group ID, and DID values) can be located on the Project Profile for your project within the Rapid Connect portal.To download a copy of the SDK zip file, click on the Download SDK Documents link within the Project Profile on the Rapid Connect site.